about.text: Hello, Im Juan Bautista Lofredo, I am 20 years old and I am from Buenos Aires, Argentina. Since I began my journey as a freelance designer over 2 years ago, I have done remote work for agencies and collaborated with talented individuals to create digital products for consumer and commercial use. I am quietly confident, naturally curious, and perpetually working to improve my skills, one design problem at a time.

proyes.bols: Bolsillo Feliz is a web application in which you can compare the prices of products in different supermarkets.
proyes.con: A web application in which you can see all the countries and grant them or see the already granted activities that can be carried out.
